{"tid":12981,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【原創廣東話音樂分享】《囑願》","createTime":"2016-11-30T01:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T15:26:42.000Z","uid":43264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"461d305179e7324ebee17cdb38b360b84c0ce87f","tid":12981,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zsZdEuKe7nY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzsZdEuKe7nY&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c2d1f1ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zsZdEuKe7nY</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首歌係送比因為至親離世而傷痛既人。假如有一日我離開呢個世界，亦希望我既親人聽到呢首歌會感到安慰。<br />\n<br />\n《囑願》<br />\n<br />\n曲：Lee Zion<br />\n詞：Rasaid Tsang<br />\n唱：Rasaid Tsang<br />\n<br />\n心   現已重新上路嗎？對吧？<br />\n離開曾依戀的牽掛<br />\n離別的淚若停不了<br />\n那讓我居於心中好嘛？<br />\n<br />\n從此上天跟心意逐漸能拉近 <br />\n奏著挽歌遙望遠方白雲<br />\n如果尚可吸口氣我願能親親你<br />\n在以後我亦會記得<br />\n承諾過一生傾聽你心<br />\n<br />\n在萬籟無聲之地跟你愛下去<br />\n若覺得不開心也不用離開   流淚沒有罪<br />\n閉上眼試著深呼吸哭夠便去睡<br />\n然後我們能一起走進夢裏<br />\n<br />\n想   若你能抛卻內心掛礙<br />\n離開亦不應該感慨<br />\n如若思念尚忘不了<br />\n你亦能讓這情感於心裡一生一世不改<br />\n<br />\n在萬籟無聲之地跟你愛下去<br />\n若覺得不開心也不用離開   流淚沒有罪<br />\n閉上眼試著深呼吸哭夠便去睡<br />\n然後我們能一起走進夢裏<br />\n<br />\n當身體沒意識連淚光都散去<br />\n當宇宙化作虛空星光引退<br />\n仍可看守你在你記憶裏<br />\n<br />\n在萬籟無聲之地跟你愛下去<br />\n若覺得不開心也不用離開   流淚沒有罪<br />\n閉上眼試著深呼吸哭夠便去睡<br />\n然後我們能一起走進夢裏<br />\n<br />\n期待我們能一起走進夢裏"},{"pid":"c6c146cd7c4d7873979c6249f7a486e5afec3e4e","tid":12981,"uid":21964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:18:44.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d53ebf6bc88419ee451818e9ca252fd883cf05","tid":12981,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位巴拉喜歡的話請比個like支持下呀！以後多D share作品！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔鐘意既話都希望比D意見，以後繼續努力"},{"pid":"a5378557461801e37d3c3e0aeb19f5b63f85405e","tid":12981,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603f7de6226d13f3f5fc38a1b880abfb655d0336","tid":12981,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"沉晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cde647fde505a93f47fe46e4e885b74a71dff0","tid":12981,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ffaba9ddd7738247a6dab8e99720b11008e5c7","tid":12981,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"頂多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}